Subject: [PATCH] redesign: restructure portfolio with hero, projects, sql
 tabs, about

- Add dark-themed Hero section with name, role, CTAs and avatar placeholder
- Add Projects section showing Olist project + upcoming placeholder
- Add dark strip divider marking entry into project detail
- Add About section with bio, tech stack tags and contact links
- Introduce indigo-600 accent color on KPI numbers, finding circles,
  project tags, primary CTAs and SQL active tab
- Replace 3 stacked SQL code blocks with tabbed SqlTabs client component
  to shorten page length
- Update nav items to follow user path
- Fix default Create Next App title and description, set lang to zh
